Sharing this with anyone who’s dreaming of moving into their DREAM HOME ❤️🧿✨ here’s what worked for me 👇#rohome 🪬

1. Journalling - I truly believe if you write it down & trust - IT WILL HAPPEN ! every morning I would write  in my journal and describe in great detail how living in my own home would feel . I’d write more about the emotions that the actual specifics of the house & describe in great detail moments of gratitude and happiness with my family like it had already happened . 

2. Visualisation- if I had 10 Mins free in the day - I’d sit down shut my eyes and visualise elements of decor,  cosy nooks,  happy moments with my family in my own house - the feeling of security happiness and abundance - visualisation is best done when you’re relaxed and in a positive state .

3 prayer & trust - even though I was asking for something specific from the universe I’d always leave the outcome to the divine source and say give me what’s best for me - give me and my family what will truly make us feel fulfilled and happy . This little element of trusting the divine is where the magic happens ✨

(ps it took me a little over a  year of dreaming and believing & taking small actions and being open to signs ) ✨

This is your sign - to start manifesting because I promise it works 🤗♥️

#rorituals #affirmations #journaling #inspiration #manifest
